title: 12/23/20 HOUR 1 - Clippers/Lakers
itunes:title: 12/23/20 HOUR 1 - Clippers/Lakers
description:
On this hour of the Dan Patrick Show, Dwayne Haskin shows that maturity is still an asset he’s yet to acquire, while being the starting QB and Captain for the Washington Football Team. NBA season opener overreaction are in and we start with the Clippers! Paul George and the Clippers looked good last night against the Lakers, but its only one game.
